  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<h2>How do product videos shorten the sales cycle for brands?</h2>
<p>Product videos shorten the sales cycle by letting customers grasp benefits instantly instead of reading long descriptions, addressing objections, and building trust before a sales conversation even starts. A recent study found that video content can speed up buying decisions by 60%, whether through a product demonstration or an explainer video.</p>
<p>The buyer's journey has evolved: customers today rely on video content to make quicker, more informed decisions, and brands that incorporate video at every stage of the customer journey can shorten the sales cycle and accelerate growth.</p>
<h2>Viven's Approach to Sales Acceleration</h2>
<p>At Viven, we help businesses achieve this through expert <a href={p("services/product-video")}>product video production</a>. We create videos that address customer objections, demonstrate real-life product use cases, and build trust — key factors in speeding up decision-making. With the right video content, brands can reduce hesitation and help customers make faster, more confident purchasing decisions.</p>
<h2>Key Deliverables</h2>
<ul>
<li>Product demonstration videos</li>
<li><a href={p("services/how-to-video")}>Explainer videos</a></li>
<li>Customer testimonial videos</li>
<li>Instructional content</li>
</ul>
<h2>Proven Impact: Meteomatics</h2>
<p>Meteomatics, a leading weather data solutions provider, partnered with Viven to create a series of explainer videos aimed at simplifying its complex product offerings for a broader audience. After launching the videos across its website and social media platforms, Meteomatics saw a significant increase in engagement and client acquisition. The videos helped shorten the decision-making process, building trust and effectively communicating the company's value proposition to new customers — see more results like this in our <a href={p("projects")}>portfolio</a>.</p>
<p>This success highlights how video content can streamline the sales process and drive faster conversions, making it an invaluable tool for businesses aiming to accelerate their sales cycles — particularly when customers need to understand a technical or unfamiliar offering before they can commit to a purchase.</p>
<h2>Why Appoint Viven as Your Video Agency</h2>
<ul>
<li>Fast project turnaround</li>
<li>Expertise in crafting sales-driven content</li>
<li>Custom solutions for both B2B and B2C brands</li>
</ul>
<p>Shortening the sales cycle is only one piece of the puzzle — pairing product videos with a broader plan for <a href={p("blog/why-brands-choose-viven-as-their-video-agency-to-drive-sales-and-build-trust")}>how brands choose their video agency</a> helps ensure every video works toward the same sales goals, rather than existing as a one-off asset disconnected from the rest of the funnel.</p>
<p><a href={p("contact")}>Work with a partner who understands your sales objectives</a> and start shortening your sales cycle with professional product video production that turns hesitant prospects into confident buyers.</p>
